 			<speak chara="_Shakespeare">"노코멘트"냐?</speak>
 			<show chara="shakesSmileClose" position="right"/>
 			<speak chara="_Shakespeare">그럼 우리 「칼레도니아호」의 승객이 될 기회를 잃을 텐데도?</speak>
 			<show chara="shakesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
 			<show chara="biankaAngryClose" position="left"/>
 			<speak chara="_Bianka">……</speak>
 			<show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left"/>
 			<speak chara="_Bianka">쳇……</speak>
 			<show chara="biankaBiteClose" position="left" opacity="0.8"/>
 			<show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right"/>
 			<speak chara="_Miguel">……그래. 만약 내가 모르길 바라는 걸 말하고 싶은 거라면——</speak>
 			<show chara="cervantesSmileClose" position="right" opacity="0.8"/>
